<h1>@HI{{iru}} (to need)</h1>

<h2> Formation </h2>

<ol>
<li> @HI{{iru}}
</ol>

<h2> Definition </h2>

<p>
@HI{{iru}}, to need, is a @5D{{}} verb and so can be distiguished in speech from
<a href="grammar-iru.html">@HI{{iru}}</a>, to be.
</p>

<p>
@HI{{iru}} uses the <a href="grammar-basic-sentence-patterns.html#waga">@HI{{ha}} ... @HI{{ga}}</a>
construction.
</p>

<h2> Examples </h2>

<ol>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{mister}}tachiha@KJ{{england^harmony^resign^code}}ga<strong>irimasu</strong>.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      You need an English-Japanese dictionary.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
<li>
<table class="sentence">
  <tr class="jp"> <td>
      @HI{{@KJ{{private}}ha@KJ{{now}}o@KJ{{gold}}ga<strong>iru</strong>.}}
  </td> </tr>
  <tr class="en"> <td>
      I need money now.
  </td> </tr>
</table>
</ol>

